{
  "stem": "27335.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I got this information from this Schandl, Karl Schandl, when he started to tell-- oh, hold it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I already heard something about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now tell me your story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told him mine, what I told you now, that the guy is circulating [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You tell me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I heard it right from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he-- and he was honest about it, that they wanted to stop the Red Army and move the Americans into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it could have been-- it could have been-- well, nobody can say anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, after all, they are allies, and the Americans got there first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the thing was that Patton, George Patton, this hardened American gangster.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was a real conniver.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He had an army, commanding the American army in Italy, and that was the plan, that he's going to lead the American army into Budapest before the Red Army gets there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it would have been-- boom, the start of the third-- because that was the-- would have been busting up the great alliance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were just half split away from Hitler winning this war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I have to make this statement and make it to many Jews-- well, look-- because there are reactionary Jews and so on-- watch this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If it wasn't for the Red Army, apart from what happened in the Soviet Union, what you say about Stalin and so on and so forth, and Bolshevism-- if it wasn't for the Red Army, there wouldn't be one Jew on this Earth today, because Hitler and his mad dog gang would have exterminated you, because we were just a step away from-- from the invasion of America.",
      "word_count": 68
    }
  ],
